value.0: Etched and oiled, the carvings on this door lend depth to its prominent woodgrain.
Etched and oiled, the carvings on this door lend depth to its prominent woodgrain.
Detailed carvings cover the surface of this finely-crafted door. The handiwork is of high quality and no doubt came at quite an expense.
Thick tallow candles burn low upon their iron stand. Small mounds have formed on the floor below, where the fallen tallow has accumulated.
A small drawer extends beneath the gleaming tabletop. It probably doubles as a desk when there's the need.

The torch paints its environs in warmer hues. You find yourself grateful for its glow.
The torch paints its environs in warmer hues. You find yourself grateful for its glow.
The wood's rich grain adds an unexpected vibrancy to this humble cabinet. Whoever crafted it clearly did so with great love.
This milky red potion seems to open the drinker's perception of his environment, making him at once more observant and more resistant to effects that target the mind.
These potions are in equal demand by adventurers and scholars, and see much use in the dungeons of Faerun.
